and I was gonna save you, and we were gonna be together.</div><ul><li> "Chuck Versus the Subway"</li></ul><div class="indent"> <strong>Stephen:</strong> This is the last time I'm gonna walk away from you.</div></li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/FryingPanOfDoom" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/FryingPanOfDoom">Frying Pan of Doom</a>: Ellie, in "Chuck Versus the Living Dead" and "Chuck Versus the Santa Suit".</li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/FullNameBasis" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/FullNameBasis">Full-Name Basis</a>: <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/BoDerek" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/BoDerek">Bo Derek</a> in "Chuck Versus Bo" (except, oddly enough, in the title). It's hilarious.</li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GatlingGood" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GatlingGood">Gatling Good</a>: Casey's <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/BigDamnHeroes" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/BigDamnHeroes">Big Damn Heroes</a> moment in "Chuck Versus the Pink Slip".<ul><li> Subverted in "Chuck Versus the Leftovers" when Volkoff's hacker disables the Buy More's gatling gun defenses.</li></ul></li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GirlWithPsychoWeapon" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GirlWithPsychoWeapon">Girl with Psycho Weapon</a>: The new 'Greta' CIA agent played by Summer Glau in "Chuck Versus the Fear of Death". She carries a small serrated knife she refers to as her "favorite friend".</li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GoofyPrintUnderwear" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GoofyPrintUnderwear">Goofy Print Underwear</a>: Casey's lucky clover boxers in "Chuck Versus the Wookiee".<div class="indent"> <strong>Carina:</strong> Like Prague again, eh Casey?</div></li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GiveAwayTheBride" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GiveAwayTheBride">Give Away the Bride</a>: Chuck and 