<h2 class="bold font-l">Chuck Failed BioChem</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Chuck attempts to save Casey by trying to give him the antidote in Chuck's body via a kiss, while a baffled Jill explains to him that's not how biology works. </p>
